snippet.title: FRU Xbox One E3 2014 Trailer
snippet.description: FRU is a classic platformer game for Xbox One with a twist. It uses the Kinect sensor to map the player's silhouette as a "mask" between two different worlds: In FRU, the protagonist is the player's movement!
